PRODUCT INFORMATION

Add new product

Login to admin section
Navigate using left hand menu to Catalog -> Products
Click the blue "Add product" plus button on the top right
Fill out the fields in the General tab (fields marked with * are required)
Fill out language tab fields (if applicable)
Click on the Data tab
FIll out required fields (price, image, model, quantity etc)
Click on Links tab
In the Categories field, start typing the name of the applicable category
Select category
Click on Attribute tab to add attributes (if applicable)
To populate attributes selecton, navigate to Catalog > Attributes
Click on Options tab to add options (if applicable)
To populate options selecton, navigate to Catalog > Options



Edit product description

Login to admin section
Navigate using left hand menu to Catalog -> Products
Click the blue edit icon beside the product you wish to edit
Edit the values required to change
Click the save icon on the top right
 
 
Change product price

Login to admin section
Navigate using left hand menu to Catalog -> Products
Click the blue edit icon beside the product you wish to edit
Click on the Data tab
Edit the price field
Click the save icon on the top right


Add special
Login to admin section
Navigate using left hand menu to Catalog -> Products
Click the blue edit icon beside the product you wish to edit
Click on the Special tab
Click the blue "Add special" plus button on the right
Set Customer Group to Default
Set Priority to 0
Add new special price in Price field
Set start and End dates of special
Click the save icon on the top right
